{"tid":371352,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣鐘意一首歌會瘋狂單曲循環","createTime":"2017-08-23T15:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T03:51:40.000Z","uid":41602,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66ea2ee5ec870758950c028bb56b01528e9577e0","tid":371352,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"呢個習慣一直都戒唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愛上一首歌之後就會不停聽，搭車聽訓教聽...聽足一個月都試過<br />\n<br />\n而最緊單曲循環既係以下呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陳穎恩唱既 時間有淚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qVgtAi-ZVIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqVgtAi-ZVIU&d=ecFjVELq14VfTjn935HzljQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0832a26b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qVgtAi-ZVIU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦都歡迎妳地放低自己近排聽既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304ea68451b0b92d12d7ea4eb69848a869367f1a","tid":371352,"uid":41602,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:53:00.000Z","msg":"推埋呢首先<br />\n<br />\n都無陳穎恩唱既 那些妳很冒險的夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rb8jxKrAzzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Frb8jxKrAzzI&d=ecFjVELq14VfTjn935HzljQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4b6810eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rb8jxKrAzzI</a>"},{"pid":"7b14184177c21787e594f04c3b6bdfbf2b72804c","tid":371352,"uid":29625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:54:42.000Z","msg":"同一隻碟loop幾年都唔厭"},{"pid":"e6a49d774351f3ed71716b5af796b1dee2c343fb","tid":371352,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同一隻碟loop幾年都唔厭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊隻 分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19795eaa260029f1130818ede574f777a9832